31:34.540 --> 31:37.490
What a strong survival instinct he has!

31:44.740 --> 31:48.910
I'm going to make your favorite
rice crackers today, Tanjiro.

31:49.160 --> 31:50.570
Wow!

31:50.830 --> 31:53.970
I'll start breaking old rice cakes first.

31:53.980 --> 31:56.390
It's our lucky day, Rokuta!
Rice crackers!

31:56.760 --> 32:01.170
No fair! Big Bro's not the only one
who likes rice crackers!

32:01.510 --> 32:03.640
- I like them, too!
- Me, too!

32:03.930 --> 32:06.590
Then, let's eat them together, okay?

32:06.930 --> 32:08.610
Can you get the grill ready for me?

32:08.610 --> 32:10.160
Okay!

32:10.440 --> 32:12.490
I'll crush them up in the grinding bowl!

32:12.490 --> 32:15.190
Okay, I'll be in charge of flipping them over, then!

32:15.190 --> 32:16.660
Me, too!

32:16.660 --> 32:19.270
Okay, then, I'll be in charge of eating them!

32:19.280 --> 32:20.940
No fair!

32:34.790 --> 32:36.370
There.

32:37.260 --> 32:39.590
Nezuko, let's go.

32:48.960 --> 32:49.940
What did I just say?

32:52.940 --> 32:54.110
I'm back!

32:56.040 --> 32:57.720
Welcome home, Tanjiro.

32:58.440 --> 32:59.910
Yeah, I'm home!

33:01.960 --> 33:03.540
Welcome home, Big Bro!

33:06.740 --> 33:08.660
Huh? Where's Nezuko?

33:08.990 --> 33:11.660
Big Sis went up the mountain
to pick vegetables.

33:12.790 --> 33:14.070
In broad daylight?

33:16.610 --> 33:18.010
She's not supposed to?

33:19.480 --> 33:20.420
Well...

33:20.760 --> 33:21.890
Um...

33:22.230 --> 33:23.090
Tanjiro...

33:23.430 --> 33:25.170
Could you get the bath ready?

33:25.510 --> 33:28.010
I'm going to be busy with this for a while.

33:31.390 --> 33:33.560
