Wake up!

34:05.380 --> 34:06.210
Wake up!

34:10.610 --> 34:11.310
Wake up!

34:11.770 --> 34:13.139
You're under attack!

34:13.480 --> 34:14.389
It's a dream!

34:14.639 --> 34:15.889
This is a dream!

34:18.060 --> 34:20.389
I see... That's right, I'm...

34:21.980 --> 34:23.560
on board the train!

34:23.980 --> 34:25.409
Wake up and fight!

34:25.830 --> 34:26.909
Fight!

34:28.080 --> 34:30.790
Fight!

34:35.330 --> 34:37.320
Big Bro, give me your pickled radishes!

34:37.330 --> 34:39.909
No, you don't! You stop it right now!

34:40.489 --> 34:43.510
Why are you always taking food away from Big Bro?

34:43.510 --> 34:44.920
What's your problem?

34:44.929 --> 34:46.760
You just had seconds!

34:49.639 --> 34:53.010
No good! I'm not awake yet!
I'm still inside a dream!

34:53.560 --> 34:55.340
How can I get out of it?

34:55.340 --> 34:57.510
Now that I've realized that it's a dream...

34:58.590 --> 35:00.520
What am I supposed to do?

35:18.340 --> 35:20.090
I have to wake up...

