Nezuko!

36:17.390 --> 36:18.390
My uniform...

36:18.730 --> 36:19.840
My Nichirin Sword...

36:20.560 --> 36:22.060
I'm waking up!

36:22.430 --> 36:23.670
Little by little.

36:24.060 --> 36:25.360
Little by little!

36:25.940 --> 36:27.240
Big Bro?

36:27.240 --> 36:29.410
Big Bro, are you all right?

36:29.410 --> 36:30.610
Big Bro?

36:31.740 --> 36:32.660
Sorry.

36:32.990 --> 36:34.360
I have to go.

36:39.240 --> 36:41.190
I have to hurry back!

36:42.960 --> 36:44.210
I'm sorry.

36:44.680 --> 36:45.620
Big Bro!

36:45.630 --> 36:47.370
- Big Bro!
- Big Bro!

36:53.710 --> 36:56.590
If the demon who's showing me
this dream is nearby...

36:57.340 --> 36:59.560
I have to find him and slash him right away!

37:01.360 --> 37:03.610
Where is he? I have to...

37:06.480 --> 37:08.140
Where are you going, Big Bro?

37:15.860 --> 37:19.040
I picked lots of vegetables today!

37:23.410 --> 37:25.210
Mom! This way!

37:25.490 --> 37:28.210
Big Bro was on fire all of a sudden!

37:31.080 --> 37:32.540
Mom?

37:32.880 --> 37:35.320
Tanjiro, are you all right?

37:36.010 --> 37:37.670
Big Bro...

37:44.390 --> 37:48.220
What's the matter, Tanjiro? Why are you dressed like that?

37:59.440 --> 38:01.270
I wish I could stay here...

38:01.610 --> 38:03.070
forever.

38:06.190 --> 38:08.460
I wish I could turn around and go back,

38:09.790 --> 38:13.960
By rights, I should've been living
like this forever.

38:14.790 --> 38:15.870
Right here.

38:17.840 --> 38:19.120
If none of this had happened...

38:19.960 --> 38:22.260
they'd'all have been alive and well now.

38:23.710 --> 38:28.640
And Nezuko would've lived in the sunlight,
under the blue sky.

38:31.480 --> 38:34.890
If none of this had happened...

38:35.980 --> 38:39.390
I should be here
making charcoal every day

38:40.440 --> 38:42.910
I never would've laid a hand on a sword!

