If none of this had happened...

38:49.630 --> 38:51.240
f none of this had happenedos

39:04.680 --> 39:07.560
But I've lost them now.

39:08.090 --> 39:09.760
I can never go back!

39:13.260 --> 39:14.670
Big Bro!

39:15.260 --> 39:17.690
Don't leave us behind!

39:24.030 --> 39:25.110
Sorry!

39:26.080 --> 39:27.740
I'm sorry, Rokuta!

39:29.530 --> 39:32.360
We can't be together anymore.

39:33.440 --> 39:37.840
But I'll always be thinking of you, okay?

39:38.710 --> 39:41.420
I'll be thinking of you all!

39:44.210 --> 39:47.290
There are lots of things to thank you for.

39:47.790 --> 39:50.770
Lots of things to be sorry for!

39:51.230 --> 39:53.160
But I will never forget you!

39:53.560 --> 39:56.890
No matter what, my heart will always be with you!

39:57.860 --> 39:58.890
So, please...

39:59.940 --> 40:01.390
forgive me!

40:08.380 --> 40:13.070
I have to destroy his spiritual core right away.

40:31.760 --> 40:34.810
